Gaming Paper, maker of fine mapping accessories and adventures for over five years, is proud to introduce the next product in the Megadungeon line. This is Megadungeon 3 "Sewers". It is 100 pages (with the potential to grow to 110 or more through stretchgoals) of geomorphic (they are compatible in many different configurations by design) maps.
